description: This file defines a service interface and its implementation for providing the latest AI trends in mechanical engineering. It includes a method that returns a list of trending topics with details such as title, summary, source URL, and date.

classes.name: ITrendsService
classes.description: Interface that declares the method for retrieving latest AI trends in mechanical engineering.

classes.name: TrendsService
classes.description: Implementation of ITrendsService that returns a static list of trending AI topics.

methods.name: GetLatestTrends
methods.description: Returns a predefined list of current AI trends specific to mechanical engineering, each with details like title, summary, source URL, and date.
